{"tid":1182675,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美銀美林調查：中國人買 iPhone 意向提升、華為下跌","createTime":"2019-06-02T10:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T15:39:58.000Z","uid":54733,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f693b25f8487137c967ba4ecc14d9645025b5163","tid":1182675,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T10:57:10.000Z","msg":"美國特朗普牽頭號召全球抵制中國華為（Huawei），難道中國人也跟隨反華為？美銀美林最新調查報告指，中國人購買 iPhone 的意向提升，反之購買華為手機的意向下跌：美銀美林分析師指中國向蘋果公司（Apple）報復的機會不大，皆因 Apple 在中國製造超過 200 萬個就業機會，倘向 Apple 報復將有很多中國人失業。<br />\n<br />\n中國人願買 iPhone 月增 3%、買華為月跌 4%<br />\n<br />\n美銀美林 5 月 30 日最新公布的「中國採購意向的調查」，對美國、英國、印度和中國等地將近 19.4 萬名買家進行消費意向進行調查。調查結果顯示，5 月份選擇 iPhone 的中國受訪者比例升至 29%，月增 3%；購買華為品牌手機的意向從 4 月份的 28% 下降至 25%。<br />\n<br />\n美國反華為，中國人撐華為情緒高漲。雖然口裡說不，身體卻很誠實。美銀美林分析師 Wamsi Mohan 在調查報告指出：「到目前為止，中國消費者購買 iPhone 的意向未減。」<br />\n<br />\nApple 創造 200 萬中國就業機會<br />\n<br />\n美銀美林分析師 Wamsi Mohan 表示，至今 iPhone 手機在中國的需求沒有受到明顯的影響。雖然無法得知中國對美國打壓將採取的回應措施，但 Apple 在中國創造 200 萬個就業機會，在中國也有超過 200 萬個蘋果應用程式開發商。如果中國對蘋果報復，可能影響民眾的工作，因此中國對蘋果展開報復的可能性較低。<br />\n<br />\n華為創辦人任正非早前接受外媒訪問時表示，若中國向國蘋果採取報復行動，他會第一個出來反對。"},{"pid":"809964d590551d1fea92fb4a46ebedf1cf2fe9f0","tid":1182675,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T10:57:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2367340/美銀美林調查：中國人買%20iPhone%20意向提升、華為下跌\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2367340%2F%E7%BE%8E%E9%8A%80%E7%BE%8E%E6%9E%97%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%B7%2520iPhone%2520%E6%84%8F%E5%90%91%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E3%80%81%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI30iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=7dcccb8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2367340/美銀美林調查：中國人買%20iPhone%20意向提升、華為下跌</a>"},{"pid":"839c3767cf1b6238dba15e06e58ca6b8121c9f0f","tid":1182675,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T10:58:21.000Z","msg":"京東618購物節手機排行榜，銷量榜apple第1名，華為才排第3名<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1182664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1182664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"adcfcde4f09b26b8d88141192416898c42a5410a","tid":1182675,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T10:59:21.000Z","msg":"中國用iphone 嘅人民特別愛國愛華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507d38e754ae809d586b5113e85447bec37b9813","tid":1182675,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T11:00:46.000Z","msg":"今年aos廿部 iPhone 無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d38e4279b97b61c39f2c8f2273ce8bd14cf311","tid":1182675,"uid":52942,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T11:01:10.000Z","msg":"華為又贏一仗，少左人買，貨源更充足，唔驚無零件"},{"pid":"0c4db7b55624c198e125b97f98aaee90518e0dee","tid":1182675,"uid":60563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"40d38e4279b97b61c39f2c8f2273ce8bd14cf311","tid":1182675,"uid":52942,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T11:01:10.000Z","msg":"華為又贏一仗，少左人買，貨源更充足，唔驚無零件"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"任正非:正中下懷，後備零件可用至萬年"},{"pid":"bb780765345e485256caa53a703f52ef18a5d2c9","tid":1182675,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5a072d8a271b59906d6c332b3c0fd208f96cbb","tid":1182675,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"唔住支那唔代表唔愛國<br />\n用iphone唔代表唔愛華為<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}